      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="d8531c772d892ebf" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>You have delved too deeply into subjects people were not meant to know. You are knowledgeable in things beyond the scope of most, but this knowledge has come at a terrible price. You are likely in questionable physical shape and occasionally shake with nervous tics. You sometimes mutter to yourself without realizing it.</source>
