      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="c7de1a2d89d83006" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Fits of Insight: Whenever such knowledge is appropriate, the GM feeds you information although there is no clear explanation as to how you could know such a thing. This is up to the GM’s discretion, but it should happen as often as once each session.</source>
        <target></target>
        <context-group name="" purpose="location">
